{"TopicId":162787,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"Sun jerks around in vessel view","CreatedByName":"RYU AZUKU99","CreatedById":150752,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-01T20:43:05Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"RYU AZUKU99","CreatedById":150752,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-01T20:43:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s been a while since Ive played ksp so I jumped on the other day and had seen that the game was updated to 1.3. I began playing and as soon as I started up a game I was on the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003Eksc\u003C/abbr\u003E screen(where you can choose buildings) and I noticed that the sun didnt move around smoothly like it always had done, it was jerking around (heres a video of it\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=icTd8nG9cpM\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=icTd8nG9cpM\u003C/a\u003E)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis issue also happens when you are in orbit around other bodies. I put a random probe in a close orbit around the sun and it still proceded to jerk around in its spot( a video for that\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://youtu.be/f3keimKkGv0\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://youtu.be/f3keimKkGv0\u003C/a\u003E)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAfter this occurred I deleted the game and redownloaded it, only to be presented with the same issues.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe videos have been taken off private\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-07-01T21:26:22Z\u0022 title=\u002207/01/2017 09:26  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 1, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by RYU AZUKU99\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tex_NL","CreatedById":58254,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-01T21:03:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoth your video\u0027s are set to private, can\u0027t view them. But I know what you\u0027re talking about. During time warp the sun does not move smoothly but jumps in small increments. All hail the glory of Squad QA. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022icon_vomit.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://www.stvvforum.be/images/smilies/icon_vomit.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-07-01T21:03:48Z\u0022 title=\u002207/01/2017 09:03  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 1, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Tex_NL\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RYU AZUKU99","CreatedById":150752,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-01T21:26:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223108492\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022162787\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221498942987\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002258254\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Tex_NL\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n23 minutes ago, Tex_NL said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoth your video\u0027s are set to private, can\u0027t view them. But I know what you\u0027re talking about. During time warp the sun does not move smoothly but jumps in small increments. All hail the glory of Squad QA. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022icon_vomit.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://www.stvvforum.be/images/smilies/icon_vomit.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFixed that. The videos are public\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-07-01T21:26:55Z\u0022 title=\u002207/01/2017 09:26  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 1, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by RYU AZUKU99\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tex_NL","CreatedById":58254,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-01T21:29:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223108516\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022162787\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221498944395\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150752\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RYU AZUKU99\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, RYU AZUKU99 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFixed that. The videos are public\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYep. That\u0027s indeed the same sun-jerking I\u0027ve been seeing since the release of 1.3.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JPLRepo","CreatedById":114736,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-01T22:01:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRead the KSP Weekly\u0027s....\u003Cbr\u003E\nOr this dev blog:\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/developerarticles.html/enter-the-shadows-r205/\u0022 ipsnoembed=\u0022false\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttp://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/developerarticles.html/enter-the-shadows-r205/\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nIn particular this post:\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/developerarticles.html/enter-the-shadows-r205/\u0026amp;page=2#comment-2610\u0022 ipsnoembed=\u0022true\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttp://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/developerarticles.